{
  "id": "RAW_877dbae4",
  "title": "首销备货 3 万台，豆包 AI 手机要卖给谁？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653092746&idx=1&sn=4776c4b8e06820cfadcf436343370360",
  "date": "2025-12-01 10:31:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"318\" data-backw=\"562\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8cu01Kavc5YuRGT3Lp6Xia9Qfz8GqKOBagT1ZZ3yWKuKnNX7ibmzpUhp3ZOJ6Xbh1VDtf2qE8uFgibku6E7m6p95Q/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-imgfileid=\"505609094\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee63c66e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5YuRGT3Lp6Xia9Qfz8GqKOBagT1ZZ3yWKuKnNX7ibmzpUhp3ZOJ6Xbh1VDtf2qE8uFgibku6E7m6p95Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjwd2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">跟中兴合作，售价 3499 元。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj17v0\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜连冉 &nbsp;张勇毅</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj5jz\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">郑玄</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj20n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">12月1日，字节跳动豆包团队发布豆包手机助手技术预览版。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1caw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">据介绍，豆包手机助手，是在豆包 APP 的基础上，和手机厂商在操作系统层面合作的 AI 助手软件。基于豆包大模型的能力和手机厂商的授权，豆包手机助手能够为用户带来更方便的交互和更丰富的体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjv05\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">现阶段，开发者和科技爱好者可以在豆包与中兴合作的工程样机 nubia M153 上，体验豆包手机助手的技术预览版本。目前该版本已面向开发者和科技爱好者少量发售，售价 3499 元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjbg6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">豆包手机助手的出现，是在试图用 AI Agent 打通APP 之间，重构移动互联网的交互逻辑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj19lg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">尽管当前的演示仍需面对技术「不确定性」的免责声明，但这种深入操作系统底层、追求「意图直达服务」的尝试，可能比单纯的 Chatbot 更具革新意义。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"332\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5751258087706685\" data-w=\"2782\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9bf4b137&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5YuRGT3Lp6Xia9Qfz8GqKOBaDrBgFq1XSJPqLykdcpKTsfKpGibJQ6Wb5o2uMjlCMUPzUO1vgUVg8rA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1w81\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">豆包手机外观设计 ｜图片来源：豆包官方</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj50v\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">或许，谁能率先解决「操作手机」的稳定性难题，谁就能定义 AI 时代的「iPhone 时刻」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjv8n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">此前，据业内人士向「极客公园」介绍，</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">字节跳动与努比亚为这款工程机的首销备货量为 3 万台，并为此订购了对应数量的手机关键元器件。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqej\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前的手机市场中，国产品牌主流旗舰，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">首销期备货通常在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">200-300 万台</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">级别。因此豆包手机虽然暂时还无法与年出货量超千万的一线手机厂商旗舰手机相提并论，但豆包手机摆脱「极客玩具」，走向更广泛的用户市场的目标已经足够清晰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj48x\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">对了，作为对比，曾经游戏手机垂直市场下的头部玩家 —— 黑鲨，在 2022-2023 年的手机出货量为 100-150 万台。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mimxs2pb1lv\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1qf2\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj143p\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mimxq7nmjcm&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">从「对话框」到「行动派」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj15r\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">过去两年，我们见惯了能写诗、能画图的 Chatbot，但对于普通用户而言，手机上最痛的痛点往往是繁琐的操作流。豆包手机助手这次的大看点，在于它试图从「对话」跨越到「行动」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj2z5\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在技术预览版的演示中，豆包展示了一种在此前 GUI Agent（图形用户界面代理）研究中常被提及的能力——它能像人类一样「看懂」屏幕，并直接模拟点击操作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj18cu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种「看懂屏幕」并模拟人类操作的底气，则源自豆包大模型在多模态能力上的积累。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjq5i\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">据官方透露，该模型在视觉理解、推理以及图像创作等维度的性能已处于国际第一梯队。正是因为模型具备了精准的图形界面（GUI）识别能力，它才能在多项权威评测中拿到高分，从而像人类一样理解「按钮」和「输入框」的含义，而不仅仅是识别一堆代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj16ty\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">据豆包手机官方使用文档介绍，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">豆包会根据意图自动判断是否调用 AI Agent 能力，若用户对话开头包含「帮我操作手机」，则会 100% 通过 AI 操作手机完成任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjglh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">任务描述越详细，它的执行效率越高，执行效果越好。例如：</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjq5i\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjglh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">打开美团外卖帮我把最近几个订单的好评写了</span><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj16ty\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mimxu7fj16ty&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjglh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">。此外，AI 操作手机是在虚拟屏操作的，不会在前台默认展开，也不会影响正在进行的其他任务，你可以随时返回桌面使用其他应用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjvkh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">用户也可以直接跟豆包对话，讲出需求，豆包可根据需求自动判断是否通过操作手机功能完成，以及在豆包对话框底部功能按钮中找到</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjvkh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">操作手机</span><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj16ty\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mimxu7fj16ty&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjvkh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">，点击按钮可手动描述需求，也可以设定定时等条件任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj12ie\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">试想这样一个场景：你在社交媒体上被种草了一款好物，过去你需要截图、退出应用、打开电商平台、搜索、比价。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而在豆包的演示中，你只需说一句「帮我在全平台比价下单」，AI 就能自动跨应用跳转，搜索同款、对比价格规格、领券，甚至帮你选好最低价的商品填入购物车。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=