、多步骤的「任务链」执行能力，可以说是 AI 从「玩具」迈向「工具」的关键分水岭之一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj3wx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">为了实现这种「类人」的交互，豆包打通了系统层面的多项权限。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj2c6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在系统层面，豆包手机为 AI 能力设计了多种交互方式，用户可以通过侧边键、语音甚至耳机唤醒它；在相册里，它能直接听懂「把路人 P 掉」的指令并执行。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"299\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5177304964539007\" data-w=\"1692\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f33df462&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5YuRGT3Lp6Xia9Qfz8GqKOBadNUPqjibsImh2ZFjKJTiceb6BGJaVg7DsT8bHsicHxvGGWiciaNetHFML5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjr1d\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：豆包手机使用指南文档</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align