ular, PingFangTC-light;\">作为「技术预览版」，豆包团队也在视频结尾特别提示，受限于大模型技术的不确定性，演示中的「丝滑」体验目前还无法百分百复现，产品距离团队的最终预期仍有差距。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj24bo\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这也体现了 AI Agent 目前最真实的状态：方向极度性感，但落地仍需时间打磨。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mimxsszz8d\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj4vu\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj5n3\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mimxq7nmpmk&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">不造硬件的「第三条路」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1zre\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在 AI 手机的浪潮中，一直存在两种流派：一种是像 Google / Pixel 手机这样，自研模型以及整套 AI 软件产品体验，并植入自家系统；另一种则是纯软件厂商，试图通过超级 APP 抢占入口。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"326\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5639312977099237\" data-w=\"2096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4360977&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5YuRGT3Lp6Xia9Qfz8GqKOBaeDeIIYQkHBGicBLC6VontA2aRZoWmw2icdeW45sKBKrbAsQwsycJfD0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1cz5\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：Google</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1y0d\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">豆包选择了第三条路：不做硬件，只做生态。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1dz3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在发布预览版的同时，豆包方面明确表示「没有自研手机计划」。他们的策略非常务实——通过与多家手机厂商洽谈，以「操作系统层面合作」的形式，将豆包的大模型能力植入不同品牌的机型中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjkl2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种「手机厂商 + 大模型厂商」的深度耦合，正在成为行业的一股新趋势。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj7y9\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">就像谷歌 Gemini 与三星的合作一样，术业有专攻正逐渐成为共识。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj2205\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">对于手机厂商而言，从零打造一个具备顶级推理、视觉理解和复杂任务规划能力的模型成本极高；而对于字节跳动这样的互联网巨头，缺乏硬件载体则会让 AI 始终隔着一层 APP 的玻璃墙，无法触达用户最核心的数据和场景。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj5nz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">目前的 nubia M153 工程机只是一个开始。售价 3499 元的门槛或许更多是面向开发者和极客人群的「邀请函」，旨在验证这种跨界合作的技术可行性与用户反馈。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mimxtfc51jcf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjbkt\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjdwl\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mimxq7nmvxt&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">光做一个APP，在 AI 时代已经不够了</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1139\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">豆包手机助手的出现，本质上或许是一次对移动互联网交互逻辑的重构。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjv5e\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">大模型的能力越来越强，单纯做一个 APP，在 AI 时代已经不够了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjnc9\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">AI Agent 需要接管更复杂的任务、感知更丰富的上下文，发挥一些真实的功能，才有更落地的价值，这意味着它必须走出软件的围墙，向下沉淀，与操作系统的底层权限和硬件能力进行深度整合。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqts\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">过往，字节跳动一直是一支强大的</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqts\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">空军</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjkl2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqts\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">——拥有极致的算法和庞大的应用生态，但在操作系统和终端硬件上，相比拥有 Android 的谷歌或拥有全场景终端的华为，字节始终缺少一块落地的</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqts\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">阵地</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjkl2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjqts\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj12q4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在移动互联网时代，这或许不是问题，但在 AI 需要深度介入用户场景的当下，缺乏硬件载体可能意味着丧失对场景的感知力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjgz8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">豆包手机助手的推出，像是字节在当下阶段抛出的一次探索</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj164d\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">从 Pico 到 Ola Friend，再到如今深入手机 OS 层的助手，字节正在小心补齐</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj164d\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">硬件触点</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjkl2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj164d\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这块短板。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjnfs\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">这或许并不是未来两三年行业的最终形态，但至少可以确认的是：</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">字节已经意识到，想要让 AI 真正跑通，必须迈出</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fj1nzz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">「</span><span leaf=\"\">软硬结合</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimxu7fjkl2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 25px 8px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">」</span><span leaf=\"\">的这关键一步。</span></strong></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "字节跳动豆包手机助手与中兴合作，通过 AI Agent 在操作系统层面重构移动交互，探索 AI 手机的软硬结合新路径。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "字节跳动豆包手机助手与中兴合作，通过 AI Agent 在操作系统层面重构移动交互，探索 AI 手机的软硬结合新路径。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了字节跳动豆包团队发布的豆包手机助手技术预览版。该产品是豆包大模型与手机厂商在操作系统层面的深度合作，旨在通过 AI Agent 实现跨应用操作，重构移动互联网的交互逻辑，从传统 Chatbot 模式转向“行动派”AI。文章详细介绍了豆包手机助手如何利用其强大的多模态能力，“看懂”屏幕并模拟人类点击，从而自动化执行复杂任务链，例如跨平台比价和旅行规划。字节跳动选择不自研硬件，而是与手机厂商深度耦合，走出了一条 AI 手机领域的“第三条路”。文章强调，AI Agent 要发挥真实价值，必须突破 APP 的“玻璃墙”，与操作系统和硬件深度整合，以感知更丰富的上下文并接管复杂任务，这是字节补齐“硬件触点”短板的关键一步。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 从“对话”到“行动”重构移动交互",
      "explanation": "豆包手机助手利用多模态大模型能力，实现 GUI Agent 功能，能“看懂”屏幕并模拟操作，自动化执行跨应用复杂任务，提升用户效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "字节跳动探索 AI 手机“第三条路”",
      "explanation": "选择不自研硬件，而是与手机厂商在操作系统层面深度合作，将大模型能力植入不同品牌机型，实现软硬结合的生态策略。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 需深度整合操作系统和硬件",
      "explanation": "文章强调，AI Agent 要发挥更大价值，必须突破 APP 的“玻璃墙”，与底层系统和硬件能力深度融合，以感知更丰富的上下文并接管复杂任务。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "豆包手机助手的出现，是在试图用 AI Agent 打通 APP 之间，重构移动互联网的交互逻辑。",
    "或许，谁能率先解决「操作手机」的稳定性难题，谁就能定义 AI 时代的「iPhone 时刻」。",
    "豆包选择了第三条路：不做硬件，只做生态。",
    "大模型的能力越来越强，单纯做一个 APP，在 AI 时代已经不够了。",
    "字节已经意识到，想要让 AI 真正跑通，必须迈出「软硬结合」的这关键一步。"
  ],
